    "description": "NCC Urban Digital Technologies is actively seeking a talented and motivated Business Development Manager to join our dynamic team in Mysuru. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout NCC Urban Digital Technologies:\nNCC Urban Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with NCC Urban Digital Technologies!",
